metadata.name: Coffee and Katie
metadata.description:
She's smart, sassy, and fierce! From DESPOP PUBLISHING IP- THE INFAMOUS KATIE ROGERS
Katie Rogers is a  British publicist working in the cutthroat world of Hollywood, trying to save the careers of her estranged clients whilst juggling her everyday life. Created in 2004, Katie has appeared in books, hosted parties, and was even optioned as a TV series.  Her motion comic book THE TROUBLE WITH KATIE ROGERS  premiered on the  Madefire motion book App and a brand new Graphic Novel is in the works.

Purchase of this piece includes an exclusive signed print
